<style>
    .reveal div .lower { text-transform: lowercase; }
</style>
<h2 class="lower">&lt;main&gt;</h2>
<div align="left">
    &lt;main&gt; is for content unique to a page.
    Use &lt;main&gt; only once per page, and put it directly inside &lt;body&gt;.
    Ideally this shouldn't be nested within other elements.
</div>